comment: I know it's bad and I'm sure people who have seen our packing videos have noticed... I use a plastic shopping bag. Which I guess is a good way to recycle them. I put the shoes in the bag in place of a packing cube bag. We've talked about getting a real bag haha but for now that's what we're rocking with. I'm definitely going to check out the jewelry case. I get rings in each country I visit. Ever since my college study abroad trip. - SE
